<div class="alert alert-secondary mb-3" role="alert">
    This example shows you how to build simple shopping carts using XcooBee pay-urls. We have added a simple script that will reload your cart i-frame as users are clicking on your links. The links can be generated.
</div>
<div class="row m-0 justify-content-center">
    <h5>Our products</h5>
</div>
<div class="row m-0">
    <div class="col-6 p-2 d-flex flex-row">
        {{#each products}}
            <div class="card m-2 product_item" style="width: 33%">
                <a href="#" class="product_link"><img class="card-img-top" src="{{this.image}}"></a>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <a href="#" class="product_link">
                        <h5 class="card-title text-center"><span class="product_name">{{this.name}}</span> - $<span class="product_price">{{this.price}}</span></h5>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        {{/each}}
    </div>
    <div class="col-6 p-2">
        <iframe id="shopping_cart"></iframe>
    </div>
</div>

